    description:
      '<p>Suchst du eine neue, spannende Herausforderung? Eine Anstellung mit starken Entwicklungsmöglichkeiten in einem der führenden Online-Unternehmen Deutschlands? Persönliche und berufliche Entfaltungsmöglichkeiten?</p>\n<p><a href="http://lampenwelt.de/">Lampenwelt.de</a> gehört zu den führenden E-Commerce Unternehmen Deutschlands und ist unter den Online-Spezialisten in seiner Branche <strong>Marktführer</strong> und Benchmark in Europa. Wir sind in <strong>17 europäischen Ländern</strong> aktiv. Mit einem Team von aktuell <strong>über 500 Mitarbeitern aus 25 Nationen</strong> schreiben wir die Erfolgsgeschichte von Lampenwelt fort – und brauchen Verstärkung.</p>\n<p><strong>Deine Aufgaben:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>contribute in architecture and other fundamental discussions</li>\n<li>implement assigned stories using the architecture and technology chosen by the team</li>\n<li>transform design layouts into state of the art mobile-first applications under consideration of our code guidelines</li>\n<li>taking care of APIs, connections to third party tools</li>\n<li>create high quality, reusable and resilient code</li>\n<li>explore and evaluate new technologies and frameworks</li>\n<li>implement all required tests to meet the „Definition of Done"</li>\n<li>help and train other engineers on their technical tasks</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Du bringst mit:</strong></p>\n<p>As a web developer by heart you:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>have a solid understanding of modern web architecture and advanced experience in a web framework like next.js, react, vuejs, node/nestjs, but also Ruby on Rails, Elixir or Phoenix</li>\n<li>have relevant experience in developing large web applications (preferably for e-commerce)</li>\n<li>have knowledge of cloud computing and how to write software in IAAS/PAAS mode</li>\n<li>have knowledge in event-drive / microservice architecture is advantageous</li>\n<li>have knowledge in test automation and CI/CD</li>\n<li>are looking for a place where you can challenge yourself, thrive and make your work time count</li>\n<li>have experience in stakeholder and time management</li>\n<li>have a deep understanding of agile work and use the know how to organize work around stories and tasks</li>\n<li>are proactive, self-reliant, self-reflective and assertive</li>\n<li>have 5-6 years of work experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Wir bieten:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Homeoffice</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Homeoffice regulation</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Employee discounts</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Special conditions on our product range</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>FlexWork</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Possibility of flexitime</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Individual development opportunities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Individual training</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>JobBike</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Contribution to your own dream bike</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Sports and fitness offers</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Special conditions for Lampenwelt employees in all fitness studios</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Entrepreneurial atmosphere</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Company events and high appreciation of employees</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Team spirit</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Meet for coffee with our CEO? Participate in the company\'s own running or soccer group? We live and breathe togetherness!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Dein Ansprechpartner:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Melissa Barnes</strong></p>\n<p>+49 6642-406 99 9930\n<a href="mailto:melissa.barnes@lampenwelt.de">melissa.barnes@lampenwelt.de</a></p>\n<p>Wir freuen uns auf deine aussagekräftigen Bewerbungsunterlagen!\n<strong>Bewerbungen bitte online unter dem Button "Bewerben" einreichen!</strong></p>\n<p><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/5802eb011c2355537029d1f0c484d96819a43a06/68747470733a2f2f742e676f686972696e672e636f6d2f682f65303163643464663330333235333466663236613264393431653533653764336565393733653432616232663334333231383031646338313932373231383139"></p>\n',
